citations.desc: ACCESS AND INSPECTION OF RECORDS AND PROPERTY; SUBMISSION OF ITINERARIES.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 1104 on
22-Jul-20.
Inspector arrival to facility at 1104 on Wednesday 22 July 2020 No sign of licensee nor personnel. Called licensee
primary contact # on phone and left voicemail message. Honked car horn. Texted licensee at 1114, no response.
Left attempted inspection note in stamped and addressed envelope and departed from facility at approx 1200.
